title: PC3 cell line - exosomes
characteristics_ch1.1: cell type: human prostate cancer cell line
growth_protocol_ch1: The cell line was cultured in serum-free medium to collect the supernatant, and the extracellular vesicles (EVs) were collected by differential centrifugation following MISEV2018 guidelines.
extract_protocol_ch1: Use miRNeasy Serum/Plasma Kit(50) Qiagen#217184 kit for RNA extraction of samples, and follow the standard operating procedure manual provided by the kit manufacturer during extraction.The extraced total RNA is the sample.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Libraries were prepared for sequencing using standard QiagenTM miRNA library construction protocol.
data_processing: The fastx_toolkit (0.0.14) software was used to dynamically remove the linker sequence fragments and low-quality fragments from the 3'end of the sequencing data.
data_processing.1: Use seqtk (1.0-r82-dirty) and self-written R (3.x.x) scripts to perform quality control analysis on the preprocessed data.
data_processing.2: Small RNA classification uses unitas software, and sequence alignment uses bowtie (1.0.0).
